cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it using the metadata below."

title: "hypergraph-functional-bounds"
abstract: >
  Julia code for computing the local (classical) and quantum bounds of the
  Bell functional associated with k-uniform complete hypergraph states, as
  constructed in the manuscript "k-Uniform complete hypergraph states
  stabilizers in terms of local operators".

version: "1.0.0"
date-released: "2025-01-01"

authors:
